Title: Lunar Cycle
Plot: After the revelation at the Pink Ride, Jodi vows to fight for Bette. Tasha and Alice look for a house together, and at work, Alice meets a New Zealander fashion designer. Adele finally reveals her master plan: to take over the movie. Finally, Dawn Denbo and lover Cindi deliver a blow that pushes Kit over the edge.
GuestStars: Amber Borycki, Melanie Lynskey, Danielle Kremeniuk, Aaron Craven, Brenda Campbell
